Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,before you get to the watcher you get to\Nthe experiences so here is the form I am
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,George and I'm 14 years old or whatever\Nand my dog is here And you say, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,this is registering in something and I'm\Nbecause I'm recognizing it and I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:16:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing it. And you begin to\Nrealize that there's a watcher of all
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,this. There's a knower of all this.\NSomehow there's a spotlight, there's a
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,lens, something is aware and you realize\Nthat there is awareness going on of the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,observer and the witness.\NAs you go beyond the observer and the
