Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiology then is that it affirms that\Nwhich has existence, that which is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the first time in human history\Ngives us a means of differentiating
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,truth from falsehood.\NThe discovery that you can differentiate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,truth from falsehood anywhere in time\Nabout anything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:20:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is so mind-boggling that I don't think\Nanybody on the planet has
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,grasped the significance of it\Nincluding myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it uh sort of blew me away for some\Nyears and uh number of people when they
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,first read the the prior the manuscript\Nmanuscript of art versus went to Europe
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,for a couple of weeks and to just\Nrecover from the shock of discovery
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that for the first time in human history\Nmankind has
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,some means of navigation\Nother than
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,credility. In other words, other than\Nfaith in others,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind has some means of telling truth\Nfrom falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you look at the history of\Nmankind, it's a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The history of mankind is really a\Ndisaster. If you don't think so, you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,watch the History Channel a couple of\Nnights and it'll change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the consciousness of mankind, you\Nknow, was was about 190 for many many
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,centuries\Nand um
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,87% of the population or 85%\Ncalibrated below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore such things as the current\Nthe current situation in the Middle East
