Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,world's been that way. All of Europe was\Nravaged by one horde after another. All
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of Asia was ravaged by one horde after\Nanother. It was just one civilization
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,plundering and savaging another\Ncivilization
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,continuously.\NAnd it goes on right up to this very
