Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.88,0:28:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness. And what we see is the\Nevolution of form. But the evolution of
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.84,0:28:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,form is only a result, a consequence of\Nthat which is evolving in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.36,0:28:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we say that is? Because we see\Nthe progression of complexity and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.60,0:29:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,function throughout the evolution of\Nlife on this planet. the smallest little
