Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.27,0:29:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The small little bacteria begins to\Nmultiply and begins to learn. So we see
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.52,0:29:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,qualities of consciousness now\Naccompanying materiality and physicality
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.76,0:29:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because learning is not something that\Nchemicals and molecules do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.48,0:29:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So\Nthe evolution of consciousness then and
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.36,0:29:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as it manifests in form we see is the\Nevolution to higher and higher forms
