Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.00,1:05:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it depends on what you set the\Npoverty level at. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.83,1:05:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh,\Nand those are a matter of many
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.68,1:05:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,gradations, expectations, and uh,\Nwhat you set the poverty level at. then
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.55,1:06:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,decides on what percentage of the\Npopulation is uh you know when I first
