Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.79,1:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you and I got silverware. I went to\Ngarage sales. So I got silverware for
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.92,1:06:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,like 50 cents and plates for a dollar\Nand I lived that way for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.03,1:06:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't need anything. Therefore, you\Ndon't have any shortage. And if you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.24,1:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have any needs, you don't have any\Nshortage, you can't experience your
