Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.48,1:07:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They heaped it up with big m things that\Nthis and then it dried and there was
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.88,1:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,they had tons of manure. For 10 bucks\Nthey would take this thing, lift it up,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.11,1:07:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,dump it in the back of your truck. Boom.\NI had a whole truckload. The back of the
