Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.72,1:08:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So you see definition then\Ndefinition.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.48,1:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand back east I can\Nremember a time when if I didn't have
