Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.12,1:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,here degrees Fahrenheit. Okay.\NWe notice there is something important.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.04,1:08:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,However,\Nif
