Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.08,1:11:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the incident after Pearl Harbor. All of\Nit changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.56,1:11:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So the context then changes the meaning\Nof content. what's appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.71,1:11:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to change content then because\Nit mean its meaning is dependent on
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.04,1:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,context. All right, context.\NIt's politically naive to pretend that
