Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.64,1:12:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,water at 32°. So if we take water and\Nbelow 32° F it's a solid above 32 it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.67,1:12:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,turns into water. Above 212 it turns\Ninto a gas. Those are very profound
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.28,1:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,changes due to shift of context.\NTechnically, the content hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.80,1:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still H2O.\NIt's still H2O. But you can't pretend
