Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.12,1:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So here at 200 then we have a critical\Nshift of quality
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.67,1:13:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that is occurring without there becoming\Nopposites.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.92,1:13:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that there's a shift to quality\Ndoes not mean that they're opposites.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.40,1:13:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,H2O is still H2O whether it's solid,\Nliquid, or gas.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.80,1:13:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can't say the dinosaur is evil. We\Ncan't say that bin Laden is evil. We
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.64,1:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,can't say that the Middle East is evil.\NThey calibrate down here. Their quality
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.04,1:13:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is considerably different once because\Nthey're below the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.60,1:13:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is above the line nurtures\Nand supports life. That which is below
