Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.88,1:13:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,matter of positionality. All description\Nis arbitrary.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.28,1:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No such thing exists in and of itself.\NIt gets you out of the hook of good
